Package it.grid.storm.api.filesystem.quota.posix

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CLibrary
    CLibrary maps the standard C library to a Java interface through JNA.
    ErrNo
    ErrNo interface maps some of the error codes contained into the standard C library sys/errno.h
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CLibrary.T_dqblk
    T_dqblk is the correspondent of the dqblk structure defined in sys/quota.h and returned by reference as addr field after quotactl() call with Q_GETQUOTA.
    PosixQuotaInfo
    The quota information associated to a block device.
    PosixQuotaManager
    PosixQuotaManager allows to access/modify the quota information on a Posix filesystem.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    PosixQuotaException
    Exception raised in case of an error.
